title: Murphy, Escobar become the latest surprise stars in October
text: > Top News Murphy, Escobar become the latest surprise stars in October FILE- In this Oct. 27, 2011, file photo, St. Louis Cardinals' David Freese reacts after hitting a walk-off home run during the 11th inning of Game 6 of baseball's World Series against the Texas Rangers in St. Louis. Freese had only 184 regular-season games of experience when he became just the sixth player to win MVP of the LCS and World Series. (AP Photo/Charlie Riedel, File)
